title: /serverless/DAYS Auckland
eventShortDescription:
/serverless/DAYS will be an in-person event, held on 24th May at the Pullman Hotel in Auckland. It's a 1-day community-run event comprised of talks and networking among active developers and technical leaders across Australia & New Zealand.

SSW & Tina are proud sponsors. We are hosting the after party, RSVP here.
Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this conference.
